x-connector-connection.validate: function(context) { const url = (context.environment === 'staging') ? 'https://api-staging.connectwisedev.com/v4_6_release/apis/3.0/system/info' : `https://api-${context.environment}.myconnectwise.net/v4_6_release/apis/3.0/system/info`; const headers = {}; headers.Authorization = `Basic ${btoa(context.companyId + '+' + context.publicKey + ':' + context.privateKey)}`; headers.ClientId = context.clientId; return context.httpRequest.get(url, { headers }); }
